{"word":"G2675 - καταρτίζω - katartízō - kat-ar-tid'-zo - Fit","slug":"G2675","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταρτίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katartízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-ar-tid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fit"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - katartizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kat-ar-tid'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G739\">G739</a>; to <i>complete thoroughly</i>, that is, <i>repair</i> (literally or figuratively) or <i>adjust:</i> - fit, frame, mend, (make) perfect (-ly join together), prepare, restore."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1822\">G1822</a>, <a href=\"#/G2676\">G2676</a>, <a href=\"#/G2677\">G2677</a>, <a href=\"#/G739\">G739</a>"}]}